{"tid":1429501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍灣連儂牆 姨姨提醒","createTime":"2019-08-07T13:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:44:11.000Z","uid":40466,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"998c08387fdc43de7e91c273563664f7c7c2f1c1","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩九龍灣連儂牆<br />\n有位姨姨提醒<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想捐物文具同食物券的話<br />\n不如考慮直接捐去星火同612<br />\n<br />\n佢話有好多人將食券放係枱上同其他暗角位<br />\n佢每日執既時候都見到有<br />\n所以驚d券比唔到真正有需要既人<br />\n如果係想比既 不如直接比前線<br />\n如果係比唔到前線 可以直接捐錢去星火同612<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果有義士拎左食券同八達通既<br />\n儘量唔好係街到大聲同人講 <br />\n因為佢聽到有師奶將有人拎左券既消息即刻打電話同人講<br />\n所以怕有黑心人亂傳作故事<br />\n同埋有d貪心既人見到人有就想要 不停追問點先有券 <br />\n所以買左券既就一係直接比前線 唔好再放係街上/比所謂義工既人<br />\n<br />\n資金唔係源源不絕的 每一分一毫都係大家夾出黎<br />\n希望大家珍惜自己既錢 留返比真正有需要既義士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係姨姨寫 佢話貼左好多日叫人唔好再捐野黎<br />\n但每日都仲好多人捐 請大家留意一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3TYMpo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3TYMpo.png&h=d65df162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"66bc612ddc7470e12247fb88d8ed10aca5a9ff59","tid":1429501,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"借推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(文宣時間)係時候吸納廢老藍絲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8297fb7bd13fbb779e06599970a837c7c6298388","tid":1429501,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"捐錢 星火 幫被捕 人仕"},{"pid":"164d4442808dddc73872fa0d047fb69729242a7c","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"唔好再周圍放券啦<br />\n一陣又比藍絲廢老話我地收錢<br />\n<br />\n姨姨有d券比唔到前線所以自己捐返相同金額既錢去612<br />\n自己再要曬d券 <br />\n佢知咁樣係浪費左有心人既初衷<br />\n但再放券就驚比人拎 同比人講閒話<br />\n<br />\n我都係代姨姨post 希望大家見諒"},{"pid":"04c26319fac21b1897ac591f72c368eda7d6e609","tid":1429501,"uid":37686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"推 我都覺得就咁放係地幫唔到有需要既人<br />\n<br />\n[蓮登仔女]長輩圖文宣組再現!!大量制作!!快啲幫手整!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc2f0167bc0247cbe0c9d8463a1aa2dd8e62c852","tid":1429501,"uid":167756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"155905a491583f0bc439a90135beb73e6a4c3d3a","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0c446fcc37d491440330288744a06712cd1b729","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a982e173ed62ffb5d240632516a3f8a96495e185","tid":1429501,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[急] 全港十八區出現武器庫丶軍火原材料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n汽油彈（英語：Molotov Cocktail，俄語：Кокте́йль Мо́лотова，意為「莫洛托夫雞尾酒」），又稱燃燒彈，是游擊隊等非正規部隊，<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以及街頭暴亂群眾的常用武器，有些罪犯也會以它來縱火。</span></strong></span></ins>軍方亦有採用，不同於制式武器凝固汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">燃燒瓶的主要構造為：玻璃瓶，</span></span><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">瓶內裝有半滿的易燃液體，例如三分之二的汽油與三分之一的油混合而成的液體或酒精（甲醇或乙醇）； 瓶口以軟木塞或塑膠、橡膠、電線膠帶、牛皮膠帶等不透氣塞堵住；瓶口上紮上布塊作引。 使用之前把布塊沾透易燃液體，燃點布塊後把瓶拋出。玻璃瓶撞擊目標破裂，易燃液體傾倒在目標之上，被火點著燃燒，可造成一定的阻絕及殺傷能力。<br />\n<br />\n蘇聯曾經製造制式汽油彈，外面裝有兩根密封有濃硫酸的玻璃管。投擲碰碎之後靠化學反應產生的熱量點燃油料，從而節省了點火步驟。<br />\n<br />\n燃燒瓶的原理跟正規軍隊使用的燃燒彈基本相同；兩者都是以汽油混合使汽油變稠的物料。<br />\n<br />\n另外也有人使用塑膠袋裝汽油，因為塑膠袋可以承載著一定容量的液體。</span></del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201404/06/P201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201404%2F06%2FP201404040808_photo_1067314.JPG&h=2cfe9af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18區陸續出現多種以綠色標誌的可疑軍火庫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/zh-hant/node5045/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode5045%2F4.jpg&h=eac93a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不知名人士正在提取疑似軍火<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20130401/large/01ls3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130401%2Flarge%2F01ls3p2a.jpg&h=74db3026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201407/20/P201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201407%2F20%2FP201407180904_photo_1071737.JPG&h=419e2799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有熱心人士幫忙抽走疑似軍火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/sites/default/files/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/waste/eco_responsibility/files/Poster_private1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fwaste%2Feco_responsibility%2Ffiles%2FPoster_private1.jpg&h=5b1cffb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可疑單張來源不明<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享 同意請按讚 好人一生平安 <br />\ntag#香港加油!#和平!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3d87b7d595f409522c249fdef6fdc7fb06f44007","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a3a27a6f0a69d8f964d613da8a127e987c79608","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca3d8f868df1043fce2c2f61cf71d2769b35d050","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c73e83ab56939c8bb0b708bb2429afd61fb63051","tid":1429501,"uid":229444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"推 好重要"},{"pid":"3e75bd53ed9233b89c320dec1f2facfa084cd5fb","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9762297af7eec8aa1c5b36c9e308210107992d50","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dccf8e6a72096dae9cb9cb63872f2b1b9786c80","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b12678bee170107d14c1cefa2054731de81420d","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7795e6808486834ac5ca48671f754f47e0029f75","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a99239dcf3d8b5b2a43b678b2d28f3a9c77f179","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5d50b0fcccaab81b53351bb18b69b5c17c83840","tid":1429501,"uid":101691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85a2f209e2db13c6391532e46fb018bc6223a849","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c87dbe961506f6e1d7cb2b19b0fdeadf1c2d6274","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:03:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17b9e6d68b1b372a4a450837a8cd2d83440c222d","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3aab5f7f5e9c9c6df972e2d499d0ce83a920ee2f","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cfb4e4ff321f0c246e961c921bcffe319230340","tid":1429501,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}